These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lemon, cranberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, fishing, chess
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, crime, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, biathlon
1. the person eating lemon is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's sport is badminton##2
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Food          | garlic      | lemon        | cranberry     |
| Hobby         | chess | fishing | dancing    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | spy       | time-travel |
| Sport         | badminton  | snowboarding      | biathlon    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, freelancer, bartender
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, family, fantasy
3 different pets are kept: rat, goldfish, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, rowing, rugby
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person watching family movies is the freelancer##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the freelancer is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the bartender##3
6. the bartender is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching family movies and the firefighter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | freelancer    | bartender | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | family | romance       | fantasy   |
| Pet           | rabbit  | goldfish   | rat     |
| Sport         | rowing | rugby       | water-polo   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, kale, cabbage
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, comedy, musical
3 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, ferret
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, boat
1. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person eating cabbage is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the person eating asparagus is between the person watching comedy movies and the person driving the boat##2
5. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the ferret is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food          | cabbage | asparagus | kale |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | crime | comedy |
| Pet           | hedgehog       | cat   | ferret    |
| Transport     | boat      | airplane   | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, drawing, cooking
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, manager, security-guard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, drama, epic
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, american, japanese
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the security-guard is the person watching drama movies##1
4. the american is on the far right##1
5. the pilot is on the right of the japanese##1
6. the american is on the right of the japanese##1
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby         | drawing  | reading       | cooking |
| Job           | security-guard     | manager      | pilot   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller | epic     |
| Nationality   | spanish      | japanese   | american     |

