.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, cola
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, firefighter, journalist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, gospel, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, indonesian, malaysian
1. the firefighter is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
4. the firefighter is on the left of the fan of house##1
5. the journalist is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
6. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the malaysian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | cola     | soy-milk   | tea         |
| Job           | freelancer | firefighter | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep      | gospel   | house            |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | malaysian  | brazilian         |

