The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, thriller, satire
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, soul, disco
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, snowmobile, skateboard
1. the person eating apple is in the middle##1
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the person eating apple##1
3. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
5. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the fan of gospel is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person eating pomegranate##2
7. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Food          | pomegranate | apple | apricot |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | drama    | satire |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | gospel   | disco    |
| Transport     | skateboard   | subway       | snowmobile |

