.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, lemonade
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, writing
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, indian, argentine
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, skateboard, airplane
1. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the indian##1
6. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the indian and the person driving the airplane##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | milk    | lemonade  |
| Hobby         | writing        | gardening   | hiking   |
| Nationality   | argentine       | indonesian    | indian |
| Transport     | airplane          | skateboard | train       |

