.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, hot-chocolate
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, blueberry, grapes
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, dutch
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, skiing
1. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating blueberry is the canadian##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the person eating grapes is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | coffee      | water  |
| Food          | blueberry     | grapes | raspberry       |
| Nationality   | canadian  | dutch    | argentine      |
| Sport         | skiing | lacrosse  | swimming |

