.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, lemonade
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, satire, animation
3 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking sprite and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade       | mirinda   | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | animation     | satire |
| Pet           | dog      | lizard | goat    |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | cycling     | tennis |

