.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, paramedic, writer
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, italian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, baseball, golf
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, roller, jet-ski
1. the photographer is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
2. the photographer is on the left of the paramedic##1
3. the paramedic is in an even position##4
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the malaysian is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
9. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic   | writer |
| Nationality   | canadian  | malaysian    | italian    |
| Sport         | baseball    | cycling | golf   |
| Transport     | roller  | jet-ski     | taxi  |

