3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is basketball is between the manager and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | cooking   | hiking      |
| Job           | manager | doctor    | project-manager |
| Nationality   | italian       | indonesian | indian      |
| Sport         | rugby         | basketball   | cycling     |

