.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-16::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, avocado, raspberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, spy
There are 3 different nationalities: british, german, canadian
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person eating garlic is on the left of the canadian##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the german##1
5. the canadian is on the far right##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the british is on the left or right of the canadian##3
8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Food          | avocado     | garlic   | raspberry     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | scientific   | mystery      |
| Nationality   | german | british | canadian    |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | motorbike   | quad-bike |

