.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, pear, mango
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, metal
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, colombian, spanish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, handball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
2. the colombian is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating mango##1
5. the spanish is in an even position##4
6. the fan of disco is the colombian##1
7. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating pear is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Food          | pear  | garlic   | mango |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | metal      | disco   |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | spanish | colombian |
| Sport         | handball | skiing   | swimming   |

