.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, project-manager, engineer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, gospel, soul
3 different pets are kept: rat, dog, turtle
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of soul is on the left of the project-manager##1
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the engineer is on the left or right of the librarian##3
6. the engineer is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Job           | librarian  | engineer | project-manager   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | soul           | r&b      |
| Pet           | turtle   | dog          | rat |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | motorbike           | car |

 